description: The ID of the location where this work was performed. Used for job site tracking and reporting. This represents a specific construction site location within a project, such as Building A, Floor 3, or Parking Lot. Large construction projects often have multiple work locations requiring separate tracking. This enables location-specific safety reporting and emergency response procedures. See [List Project Locations](https://developers.procore.com/reference/rest/v1/locations#list-project-locations) to retrieve available locations for your project.
